@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}

<!-- Main body -->
  <div id="main">
    <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel" style="max-height: 300px; position:relative;z-index:1;">
      <!-- Indicators -->
      <ol class="carousel-indicators" style="z-index:1 !important">
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
        <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
      </ol>

      <!-- Wrapper for slides -->
      <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
        <div class="item active" style="max-height: 300px;">
          <img src="~/images/Kimi no na wa.jpg" alt="Kimi no na wa" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h3>Kimi No Na Wa</h3>
            <p>One day, Mitsuha awakens in a room that is not her own and suddenly finds herself living the dream life in Tokyo—but in Taki's body! Elsewhere, Taki finds himself living Mitsuha's life in the humble countryside. In pursuit of an answer to this strange phenomenon, they begin to search for one another.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="item" style="max-height: 300px;">
          <img src="~/images/Jigsaw.jpg" alt="Jigsaw" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h3>Jigsaw</h3>
            <p>Bodies are turning up around the city, each having met a uniquely gruesome demise. As the investigation proceeds, evidence points to one suspect: John Kramer, the man known as Jigsaw, who has been dead for ten years.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="item" style="max-height: 300px;">
          <img src="~/images/Justice League.jpg" alt="Justice League" style="width:100%;">
          <div class="carousel-caption">
            <h3>Justice League</h3>
            <p>Fueled by his restored faith in humanity and inspired by Superman's selfless act, Bruce Wayne enlists the help of his newfound ally, Diana Prince, to face an even greater enemy.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Controls -->
      <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
      </a>
      <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <br>
    <br>

    <!-- Container -->
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Row -->
      <div class="row">

        <!-- Column -->
        <div class="col-xl-4 col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
