          <div class="shopping-grid">
            <!-- Image -->
            <a href="#">
              <img class="img-responsive img-thumbnail" src="~/images/Professor Marston and the Wonder Women.jpg">
            </a><!-- /.img -->
            <!-- Caption content -->
            <div class = "caption text-center">
              <!-- Content Header -->
              <h3>Professor Marston and the Wonder Women</h3>
              <!-- Content paragraph -->
              <p>Professor Marston and the Wonder Women is a 2017 American biographical drama film about American psychologist William Moulton Marston, who created the fictional character Wonder Woman. The film, directed and written by Angela Robinson, stars Luke Evans as Marston, Rebecca Hall as his legal wife Elizabeth and Bella Heathcote as Marston's live-in mistress, Olive Byrne. JJ Feild, Oliver Platt and Connie Britton also star.
                The film premiered at the 2017 Toronto International Film Festival and was released in the United States on October 13, 2017. It received positive reviews from critics, who praised Robinson's direction and the performances of its stars.
              </p>
